				<td colspan="2"><span>I second the Everfrost camp/North Ro with a couple exeptions
<br />

<br />
the augments can be found to add to the armor at any camp, or indeed other items. If that's what you want, you may want to eventually at least get half or all of your max points at each camp. Depends on if you just want armor or the best LDON gear in all categories.
<br />

<br />
Not to run Paeros down or anything, but I consider LDON with ALL augments to be a step between the Ornate and the Elemental/Time gear. It's not really comparable.
<br />

<br />
In my opinion LDON is what you go for if you do not expect your guild (or you personally) to get the &quot;Real Gear&quot; anytime soon. Or you can get it as backup/interim gear.</span></td>
