				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Most Desirable LDoN for Bards?<a name="15682"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 14 04 6:41 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I have said many times that when it comes to LDON armor, be very critical of the stats.  Yes, the Royal Attendant from Tak has the most AC in every case. But the Malevolent Greaves and Malevolent Vambraces come with stamina and charisma and their counterparts in Takish do not -- which means the Miragul pieces for arms and legs are MUCH better buys at half the price and better pre-augmented stats, overall.  Ideally, if you are outfitting yourself with armor from LDON, you will want some of both but study the stats -- it will affect your decsions.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
