				<td colspan="2"><span>The Malevolent greaves are better.  Sorry to disagree with you but they just are.  The TOTAL Hp (including from STA) are higher and the added CHA is essential at higher levels.  Trading off 4 AC and some less meaningful stats to save 732 AP and at the same time gain HP and CHA -- believe me, they are a much better deal.  As for the arms -- I think the savings in AP are worth the difference.  That's an opinion I can see some disagreement with, but assuming you're earning 51 per mission and spend a minimum of one hour forming group and doing the mission, you're talking 14 hours of hard work and the sleeves are just not 14 hours of MY time better at Takish.</span></td>
